Elle Macpherson, 58, stunned in a beige long-sleeved dress during the Paris Haute Couture Fashion Week 2022. The dress featured a high-collar and sheer detailing, leaving Elle to cut a stylish figure, while showing off her famous supermodel body. She styled her signature blonde tresses in voluminous curls and complimented her outfit with a pair of black sunglasses. The Friends actress was accompanied by her handsome son Arpad Flynn, 24, who looked dapper in a black suit and white shirt. Elle shares her lookalike son Flynn with her former partner, Arpad Busson. They began dating in 1996 and had two sons together before breaking up in 2005.